ActHeritage Railway Stations Protection Act
SubjectCanadian Pacific Railway (Lacolle Station) ** Sale **
PrecisOrder authorizing the CANADIAN PACIFIC RAILWAY COMPANY to sell its station building in LACOLLE, Quebec, to the Municipality of Lacolle in a manner that provides for continuing protection of the heritage character of the station once it is no longer under the protection of the Heritage Railway Stations Protection Act.
